<ul><li><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Iceflow-2009-01-04T18:27:00.000Z-Rgoodermote's_Rules"></span>If it works, let it be. It isn't the process merely the person</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:ANI" class="mw-redirect" title="Wikipedia:ANI">AN/I</a> and <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:AN" class="mw-redirect" title="Wikipedia:AN">AN</a> are not for personal complaints. (unless it is serious)</li>
<li>When everyone tells you that you are wrong. You are wrong.</li></ul>
<dl><dd><dl><dd>See <a href="https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Don%27t_be_a_Dick" class="extiw" title="m:Don't be a Dick">Don't be a dick</a> on Meta. "If you've been labeled as a dick, especially if you have been told this by several people in a particular community, it might be wise to consider the possibility that it is true." <a href="/wiki/User:Iceflow" title="User:Iceflow">Thor Malmjursson</a> (<a href="/wiki/User_talk:Iceflow" class="mw-redirect" title="User talk:Iceflow">talk</a>) 18:27, 4 January 2009 (UTC)<span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Iceflow-2009-01-04T18:27:00.000Z-Rgoodermote's_Rules"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">reply</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2009-01-04T18:27:00.000Z","author":"Iceflow","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-Iceflow-2009-01-04T18:27:00.000Z-Rgoodermote's_Rules","replies":["c-Rgoodermote-2009-01-05T15:10:00.000Z-Iceflow-2009-01-04T18:27:00.000Z"],"displayName":"Thor Malmjursson"}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Iceflow-2009-01-04T18:27:00.000Z-Rgoodermote's_Rules"></span>
