<ul><li>How do you define idiot? <a href="/wiki/User_talk:Garden" class="mw-redirect" title="User talk:Garden"><font color="#cc3333"><b>Garden</b></font></a>. 21:17, 6 January 2009 (UTC)<span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Garden-2009-01-06T21:17:00.000Z-Pee_Tern-2009-01-08T13:03:00.000Z"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">reply</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2009-01-06T21:17:00.000Z","author":"Garden","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-Garden-2009-01-06T21:17:00.000Z-Pee_Tern-2009-01-08T13:03:00.000Z","replies":["c-Gurch-2009-01-06T21:41:00.000Z-Garden-2009-01-06T21:17:00.000Z"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Garden-2009-01-06T21:17:00.000Z-Pee_Tern-2009-01-08T13:03:00.000Z"></span>
